This place is Great! from the staff to the food everything is great here. i had the half roasted chicken with glazed pomegranate sauce on top it was amazing & i also had a hookah for the first time it was definitely something i'd come back to do again. Everything came out on time and i really enjoyed myself i would definitely come back here also i noticed that the staff is very kind and caring to all of your needs and are always around to answer your questions or help you with any concerns you may have Mediterranean has it all and i will defiantly be back!.
